channel.title: Rune-Evo Ticket Command Doesn't Work?
channel.description: Hello! So when i am typing ::Ticket it says do ::Ticket to teleport to the player, now when i do that, it says another ticket has been requested, type ticket to answer and shit.... HOW DO I FIX THAT?? PLEASE COMMENT FAST ^.^

item.title: Rune-Evo Ticket Command Doesn't Work?
item.dc:creator: @pax_magenz pax magenz
item.description:
@pax_magenz wrote:

gimpie:

If your servers online ::ticket was ment to be used by players to sugest help from staff, that explains the type ticket to answer becuz if your servers not online theres no players to type ::ticket, now if you want to change ::ticket to recieve vote tickets or what ever your planing on using it for then id suggest you go to (rune evo source is the same one im using) your player commands and change it there or in your admin commands, donator etc. hope this helps, if not im sure theres something that can be done

My server is online, and i am using Rune-Evo Source lmao.
